{"type":null,"faqId":44327,"title":"手机与华为手机助手连接后，不能通过助手发送短信?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>由于Android 5.0及以上版本的安全机制，需要在手机上设置手机助手为默认短信应用，否则不能通过手机助手对短信进行操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当通过助手发送短信时，会有如图1-a的弹框，同时手机端有如图1-b的弹框。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157809\" style=\"width:4.9090276in;height:3.5173612in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>图1-a</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157810\" style=\"width:3.7291667in;height:6.6256943in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>图 1-b</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时需要在手机端点击“是”将助手设置为默认短信应用，同时在PC端点击确认，方可使用助手发送短信。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果需要通过手机对短信进行操作，将“短信”设置为默认短信应用，否则无法操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在手机上打开短信，如图1-c，点击顶端提示，选择“是”后，即可通过手机对短信进行操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157811\" style=\"width:3.8743055in;height:6.8951387in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":2,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9827","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400461000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":289,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"hisuite,手机助手","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}